Package org.biojava.nbio.ontology.obo

Class OboFileParser

java.lang.Object
org.biojava.nbio.ontology.obo.OboFileParser
public class OboFileParser extends Object
A class to parse the content of an OBO file. It delegates handling of the content to the OBOFileEventListener implementation. This file contains parts of the OBO-Edit file OBOParseEngine, (particularly the encoding and decoding part) See link Thanks to the OboEdit developers for giving permission to release this in BioJava.
Since:
1.6
Author:
Andreas Prlic, John Day Richter
